data.name: RichTextBox6.Text
data.value: We delightfully offer the passengers our convenient services. Merc Bus Online Ticketing Services offers bus tickets at most affordable prices that you may choose from variety of destinations around different parts of Luzon, Philippines. We provide a better experience for our customers to have an easy and quick access to our services. We offer a hassle-free booking experience that surely customers will accomplish in a few easy clicks or taps and you are set to go on your destination. Just get started, book and finish.

data.name: RichTextBox1.Text
data.value: MERC BUS is an online ticketing service which allows our passengers to purchase a ticket via online for their transportation within Luzon areas. This is a newly operating online bus ticketing platform that was established on April 2021 by a group of outstanding Grade 12 Computer Programming students from University of Makati. It aims to provide a reliable travel partner, great services, comfortable and safe journeys and excellent customer satisfaction to our valued passengers.

data.name: RichTextBox3.Text
data.value:
Bulk Package:
Price list for Bulk Packages or additional belongings such as luggages, boxes or items to be transported aside from your hand baggage:
Bus Type A. Ordinary - PHP 150 Bus Type B. Class A - PHP 300 Bus Type C. Class B - PHP 250 Bus Type D. Class C - PHP 200
Note: The price above is per passenger which depends on the bus type.
Travel Insurance:
This is an optional service which provides the passenger a peace of mind and assurance to receive a compensation in case there is a trip irregularities or even encountered in an emergency situation. You may contact our customer service support to get an updated information regarding our travel insurance.
Travel Insurance cost per bus type:
Ordinary P175 Class A P450 Class B P350 Class C P250

data.name: RichTextBox2.Text
data.value:
Fare Exceptions:
A. For a passenger with an age of 10 years old or below, the fare price is 5% off. B. For a senior citizen, there will be a 20% fare deduction. C. For a group reservation with 5 persons or above, a 5% discount is offered.
Note: Senior citizen passengers are the only ones exempted from 12% percent VAT charge.

data.name: RichTextBox4.Text
data.value:
• NOTIFICATION TO PASSENGER
- During booking, you will be asked to provide your email address and mobile number. Rest assured that your contact details are only used for your travel purpose only.
- An SMS notification will be sent to you an hour before your time departure for any update regarding your trip.
- In case of emergency, your emergency contact person will be notified.
• CANCELLATION/REFUND
1)Passenger Voluntary Cancellation:
In case of voluntary cancellation of the passenger's ticket, please see the details below.
-Cancellation within 24 hours after booking will guarantee the full refund of your payment.
-Cancellation between 25 hours after booking and 72 hours prior to your scheduled trip will be guaranteed 50% refund of your payment.
-Cancellation within 72 hours prior to your scheduled trip will have no refund on your payment.
2) Passenger Involuntary Cancellation:
In case the bus operator decides to cancel the trip, the passenger is guranteed to receive a full refund of their payment. Otherwise, the passenger will have the option to rebook again the trip for free of charges. Please see the details below for rebooking information details.
You may cancel your trip online using your MERC account. For a refund/cancellation request, kindly contact our customer service via email at customerservice@merc.com.
• REBOOKING
1) For voluntary rebooking, a rebooking fee of (PHP 50) will be applied and an additional fare to pay depending on the bus routes.
2) For involuntary rebooking, you have the option to rebook your trip for the same routes without an additional charge.
You may rebook your bus trip online using your MERC account. For rebooking request, kindly contact our customer service via email at customerservice@merc.com.
• COMPENSATION
You may contact our customer service for a compensation request in case of trip delay/cancellation or service issue. They will review your case and contact you as soon as possible. Please be advised that compensation is possible only if you have a trip insurance requested during booking. Compensation may vary depending on the policies related to your case.
